\N<Segi>Are you being cautious of me...? As if I'm an enemy who
would hurt you...
\N<Segi>But... I'm sorry. Whatever it is, I can't understand you.

\N<Segi>Right now, I don't have the luxury to care about you. I have
to overcome you all... to become stronger.

\N<Segi>I don't really understand, but... this creature also seemed
a bit strange. Maybe it was protecting this...

\N<Segi>I managed to get back this time, but... there's no guarantee
it will always go this smoothly.

\N<Segi>If a monster with a hard carapace like the one before
appears, I probably won't be able to defeat it with my
current strength...
\N<Segi>That's right, maybe Rozaro-san can help me somehow...

\N<Segi>But... before that, I need to change out of these clothes. I
can't go out in public dressed like this...

attacks are being blocked by that creature's... h-hard
carapace...!

\N<Segi>Anyway... I can't keep this up. I should head back to town
for now...

\N<Segi>Somehow I managed to return, but... what should I do from
here...

\N<Segi>No matter how many times I try, with my current strength, I
probably won't be able to defeat that creature...
